Organics gasped as Elita proceeded to make a mess.
"No, no, you must not make a mess like this!  What will your mother 
say?"
She starts cleaning up the food flying everywhere, and then takes the 
food jars and sets them on another table.  When she turns around, she 
almost knocks the table over with her wings, shield, and sword.  She 
catches it, and sits back down by Elita.  She hands the baby the 
bottle, smiling the whole time.
"Hee you go, try not to make a mess this time, please?"
